QRX:trusts QRX:Security, QRX:X509 ;
QRX:knows QRX:HAX0R, QRX:C0DE .

QRX:NSA a QRX:Mystery ;
QRX:label "NSA" ;
QRX:image "/avatar/NSA.png" ;
QRX:comment "NSA is a covert activist" ;
rdf:value "NSA, the Overseer, monitors and safeguards national security from the shadows." ;
